{"tid":2292259,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺旺入主染紅 沒有報道反送中","createTime":"2020-11-19T10:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T12:03:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"38287dc4c489e24b69f33d65319d464b17b92bd4","tid":2292259,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:57:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201119/RWDHRG7C2ZFJBNN34XH6BCDUJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201119%2FRWDHRG7C2ZFJBNN34XH6BCDUJI%2F&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopeEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=f887bc5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201119%2FRWDHRG7C2ZFJBNN34XH6BCDUJI%2F&h=eb938bbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201119/RWDHRG7C2ZFJBNN34XH6BCDUJI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n旺旺入主染紅 沒有報道反送中<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Fj32a5Y5rzkvB3hT0N8cLpZr9_A=/802x513/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J4ESFJNABRFDNFX4BMHDQSGKOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFj32a5Y5rzkvB3hT0N8cLpZr9_A%3D%2F802x513%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ4ESFJNABRFDNFX4BMHDQSGKOU.jpg&h=95ad22a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡衍明<br />\n<br />\n.......................。而旺旺中國集團去年被台媒指，近11年領取152億新台幣（下同，約41億港元）補貼，不過蔡衍明早前出席續牌聽證會時就否認曾收取補助。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n捧韓國瑜 被嘲「韓天電視台」<br />\n<br />\n2002年，中時集團接手經營中天電視台。與中國大陸關係密切的旺旺集團創辦人蔡衍明在2008年，斥資204億（約55.5億港元）收購中時。入主後，中天新聞台立場被指親中色彩濃厚，內容偏頗。<span class=\"orange\">例如去年6月9日香港反送中百萬人大遊行，中天是全台灣唯一沒有報道的新聞台。</span>自台灣2018年九合一選舉後，因大量報道前高雄市長韓國瑜的新聞，包括韓穿襪子睡覺、拿酒杯的姿勢、韓國瑜是男版林志玲等內容，而被網民戲稱為「韓天電視台」。去年2月11至17日午間與晚間新聞時段，中天出現韓國瑜姓名秒數比率一度高達56.7％。<br />\n<br />\n中天新聞台部份新聞被NCC裁定違背事實或新聞專業與倫理，違規25次，受警告處分2件，受罰鍰處分23件，總額達1,153萬元（約313萬港元），冠絕台灣。例如去年題為〈異象？！三市長合體，天空出現「鳳凰展翅」雲朵〉等報道，被指違反事實查證原則。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"e753299eb2e3d99c0b17b2f2ca31261d0f683939","tid":2292259,"uid":94279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:41:10.000Z","msg":"屌明明就係實行selfcensorship嘅lamestream media 成班友喺twitter話言論自由唔可以搞佢<br />\n<br />\n真係放虎歸山"},{"pid":"a89c787d683fbe281241cfe6607499bbe363b51f","tid":2292259,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:42:22.000Z","msg":"牌都釘撚埋<br />\n<br />\n係咪 TOTAL LOSS？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89d13de3fe0dcd657d42d204d002d0ef4ac54cf","tid":2292259,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:47:21.000Z","msg":"執七咗佢啦"},{"pid":"65ee368fe742c055ad229cb7c8d4d9d62bb64c49","tid":2292259,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T12:03:28.000Z","msg":"「內容偏頗」都死得<br />\n遲啲港共都可以禁蘋果日報出版"}]}